\newlabel{fig:fig43}{{4.40}{104}{\texorpdfstring {\xpg@aux {\xpg@current@opts }{\languagename }}{}\ignorespaces Training loss (MSE) and accuracy for Mamba-2 (+LN scaled\_tanh). The model converges within approximately 5 epochs and stabilises, with validation accuracy closely tracking training accuracy --- indicating minimal overfitting}{figure.caption.124}{}}
