\newlabel{fig:fig44}{{4.41}{105}{\texorpdfstring {\xpg@aux {\xpg@current@opts }{\languagename }}{}\ignorespaces Training loss and accuracy for Mamba S6 (+CSI tanh). The CSI-augmented input produces a smooth, monotonic training convergence, with the additional channel-state feature providing clear gradient signal for the optimizer}{figure.caption.125}{}}
